author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: Tiliqua is a modular FPGA-based platform for Eurorack systems, launched on CrowdSupply. It supports real-time audio and video synthesis using open-source tools like Amaranth HDL, offering more flexibility and performance than typical microcontroller-based modules. The platform uses the “SoldierCrab” FPGA System-on-Module, which integrates an LFE5U-25F FPGA, PSRAM, a USB PHY, and SPI flash. This module […]
title: Tiliqua Brings FPGA-Based Audio and Visual Tools to Eurorack Systems

author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: HydraLink is now available on CrowdSupply as a compact and open-source USB-to-Automotive Ethernet adapter intended for engineers, researchers, and others working with in-vehicle networks. It supports both 100BASE-T1 and 1000BASE-T1 over single-pair Ethernet, enabling direct access to automotive Ethernet without the need for media converters or additional lab equipment. HydraLink allows real-time packet forwarding between […]
title: HydraLink Offers Open USB-to-Automotive Ethernet Interface for Testing and Diagnostics

author: Giorgio Mendoza

title: VP2430 Vault Pro Featuring Intel N150 and 4x 2.5GbE in a Fanless Design
